# Story 4.1: List Pending Services

## Story Metadata
- **Epic:** 4 - Allocation with Recommendations
- **Status:** done
- **Implemented:** 2025-12-28
- **Session:** SESSION-004

## User Story
As **Diana (Dispatcher)**,
I want **to see a list of services needing train allocation**,
So that **I can prioritize my work for today/tomorrow**.

## Acceptance Criteria

| AC | Criteria | Status |
|----|----------|--------|
| AC1 | List shows services without assigned train | PASS |
| AC2 | Date filter for today/tomorrow/week | PASS |
| AC3 | Service details visible (code, route, time) | PASS |
| AC4 | List sorted by departure time | PASS |

## Implementation Details

### Files Created
- `apps/web/src/components/allocation/AllocationPanel.tsx` - Main component

### Service List Design
| Column | Content |
|--------|---------|
| Service | Code and route |
| Departure | Time and station |
| Distance | Km for the service |
| Status | Pending/Assigned |

### Filter Options
- Today (default)
- Tomorrow
- This week
- Custom date range

## Dev Notes
Service list is entry point for allocation workflow.
Diana selects a service, then sees recommendations.

